<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Portfolio | Chris Centrella</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="author" content="Chris Centrella">
    <meta name="description" content="Christian web designer, software engineer">
    <meta name="keywords" content="Chris Centrella, christian, web, designer, developer, software, engineer, website">
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
    <%= javascript_importmap_tags %>
  </head>
  <body>
      <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero-image">
          <div class="hero-overlay">
            <h1 class="logo-large">Chris<br />
              Centrella</h1>
            <div class="flex">
              <h2 class="logo-tagline">Software Engineer</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-about">
          <h1>About Me</h1>
          <p class="large">
            I’m an aspiring software engineer. I especially love creating user interfaces, because it allows me to
            uniquely
            express what matters most—to myself, my clients, or my company.
          </p>
          <div class="button-div">
            <%= link_to "Work Experience<i class='icon fa fa-chevron-right'></i>".html_safe, about_path, class: 'button' %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <main>
      <h1>Vision</h1>
      <p class="large">
        To bring the love and healing of Jesus to His children, through technology.
      </p>
      <div class="button-div">
        <%= link_to "Mission Statement<i class='icon fa fa-chevron-right'></i>".html_safe, mission_path, class: 'button' %>
      </div>
      <h1>Captivate</h1>
      <p class="large">
        It’s my passion to capture the moment through the gift of photography. Beautiful things bring hope and light
        to
        those who are depressed. Photography allows me to capture and preserve what’s beautiful. </p>
      <div class="button-div">
        <%= link_to "Photo Gallery<i class='icon fa fa-chevron-right'></i>".html_safe, photos_path, class: 'button' %>
      </div>
      <h1>Love</h1>
      <p class="large">
        Naked on the cross, Jesus cried out to His Father to have mercy on those who killed Him: “Father, forgive
        them,
        for they know not what they do.” Likewise, Jesus calls me to love each of His children, no matter what they
        have
        done or where they have been.</p>
      <div class="button-div">
        <%= link_to "Personal Blog<i class='icon fa fa-chevron-right'></i>".html_safe, blog_path, class: 'button' %>
      </div>
      <h1>Get in Touch</h1>
      <p class="large">
        Do you need assistance from a web designer or software engineer? Please don't hesitate to reach out to me and I will do my best to get back to you!
      </p>
      <div class="button-div">
        <%= link_to "Contact Me<i class='icon fa fa-chevron-right'></i>".html_safe, contact_path, class: 'button' %>
      </div>
    </main>
    <%= render 'layouts/footer' %>
  </body>
</html>
